{
  "displayName": "happy-feed",
  "mosaicLayout": {
    "columns": 12,
    "tiles": [
      {
        "xPos": 0,
        "yPos": 0,
        "width": 3,
        "height": 4,
        "widget": {
          "title": "Embedding cost (window) — calculated*",
          "scorecard": {
            "timeSeriesQuery": {
              "timeSeriesFilter": {
                "filter": "metric.type=\"workload.googleapis.com/happy_feed_embed_cost_usd\" resource.type=\"generic_node\"",
                "aggregation": {
                  "perSeriesAligner": "ALIGN_DELTA",
                  "crossSeriesReducer": "REDUCE_SUM"
                }
              }
            },
            "sparkChartView": {
              "sparkChartType": "SPARK_LINE"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "xPos": 3,
        "yPos": 0,
        "width": 3,
        "height": 4,
        "widget": {
          "title": "Embedding cost / min — calculated*",
          "xyChart": {
            "dataSets": [
              {
                "timeSeriesQuery": {
                  "timeSeriesFilter": {
                    "filter": "metric.type=\"workload.googleapis.com/happy_feed_embed_cost_usd\" resource.type=\"generic_node\"",
                    "aggregation": {
                      "alignmentPeriod": "60s",
                      "perSeriesAligner": "ALIGN_DELTA",
                      "crossSeriesReducer": "REDUCE_SUM"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "plotType": "LINE"
              }
            ],
            "yAxis": {
              "scale": "LINEAR"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "xPos": 0,
        "yPos": 4,
        "width": 12,
        "height": 2,
        "widget": {
          "title": "About the cost numbers",
          "text": {
            "content": "**Embedding cost is calculated, not billed.** Estimated as `ceil(chars / 4)` tokens × **$0.00015 / 1K tokens** (Vertex Gemini embeddings online tier, gemini-embedding-001).\n\nNot included in this dashboard:\n- **Cloud SQL bsky-db** (pgvector HNSW index + posts) — db-custom-1-3840 dedicated CPU, billed per instance type\n- **Cloud Run worker** — **~$70/mo** with 2 vCPU + 2 GiB always-on (`--no-cpu-throttling`, `--min-instances=1`)\n- **Cloud Run server** — **<$5/mo** at <10 users\n- **Cloud SQL feed-db** — billed per instance type\n- **GCS storage** — **<$5/mo** (parquets + cursors)\n\nFor actual billing (24–48h lag), see [Cloud Billing console](https://console.cloud.google.com/billing).",
            "format": "MARKDOWN"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "xPos": 0,
        "yPos": 6,
        "width": 12,
        "height": 1,
        "widget": {
          "title": "Consumers (postConsumer / engagementConsumer / profileConsumer)",
          "text": {
            "content": "Per-consumer queue depth, cursor lag, throughput, and failure rates.",
            "format": "MARKDOWN"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "xPos": 0,
        "yPos": 7,
        "width": 6,
        "height": 4,
        "widget": {
          "title": "Cursor lag by consumer (microseconds behind real-time)",
          "xyChart": {
            "dataSets": [
              {
                "legendTemplate": "${metric.label.kind}",
                "timeSeriesQuery": {
                  "timeSeriesFilter": {
                    "filter": "metric.type=\"workload.googleapis.com/happy_feed_cursor_lag_us\" resource.type=\"generic_node\"",
                    "aggregation": {
                      "alignmentPeriod": "60s",
                      "perSeriesAligner": "ALIGN_MEAN",
                      "crossSeriesReducer": "REDUCE_MEAN",
                      "groupByFields": [
                        "metric.label.kind"
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                },
                "plotType": "LINE"
              }
            ],
            "yAxis": {
              "scale": "LINEAR"
            }
          }
        }
      },
